
Summary:
Upgrade the system for high-volume, fault-tolerant file processing using Azure. Leverage Azure Queues and Blob Storage for efficient message handling, file transfer, and service integration. Ensure reliability, state management, and delivery tracking.

Key Points:

Scalable Azure app using Queue Storage

Fault-tolerant message processing

File fetch, process, and return via Queue + Blob

Duplicate handling and retry on failure

Maintain state across backend services

Blob Storage integration for seamless file access

Track processing via message IDs or URLs






